The evidence with the title 'Loggers accidentally cut down oldest tree ' says Dec 13, 2014  ...  ... A story from fake news site World News Daily claiming that loggers had accidentally cut down the world 's oldest tree in the Amazon forest . The tree was said to have been a giant Samauma tree over 5,800 years old and 40 meters  ... As with everything published by World News Daily , the story was not true . 
